title: Flatten nested cases in do-notation with pattern match alternatives.
pid: 82652a37-1769-48c5-b876-7e16d0a0eb46
body: |2-
  readNumbers : IO (Maybe (Nat, Nat))
  readNumbers
    = do Just x_ok <- readNumber
              | Nothing => pure Nothing
         Just y_ok <- readNumber
              | Nothing => pure Nothing
         pure (Just (x_ok, y_ok))
